main event: A bright, round object was observed traveling at high speed in Suffield, Ohio on December 12, 1967. The observer heard a 'beep' and saw flashing lights.
interesting points: The object was described as a bright, round object.
The object was traveling at a high speed.
The observer saw flashing lights on the object.
The Air Force requested the observer to complete an AF Form 117 to provide more information for investigation.
